android.content
接口 DialogInterface.OnClickListener

所有已知实现类：
DatePickerDialog, DialogPreference, EditTextPreference, ListPreference, Spinner, TimePickerDialog
正在封闭接口：
DialogInterface
public static interface DialogInterface.OnClickListener

Interface used to allow the creator of a dialog to run some code when an item on the dialog is clicked..

方法摘要
 void onClick(DialogInterface dialog, int which)
          This method will be invoked when a button in the dialog is clicked.
 

方法详细信息

onClick

void onClick(DialogInterface dialog,
             int which)
This method will be invoked when a button in the dialog is clicked.

参数：
dialog - The dialog that received the click.
which - The button that was clicked (e.g. DialogInterface.BUTTON1) or the position of the item clicked.
